node.text: FOR SALE. 2021 Avalanche 44ft 2 bed 2 bath house on wheels. Honestly I feel bad for whoever needs a 5th wheel and hasn’t seen this post because they’re losing $20k if they buy a different one. $53k. Model is 390DS. $2k deposit holds it for one week. Located near Nashville TN. Only needs your own couch and table installed. The stock ones were removed for a full size couch.
